<p>Alerts are suitable for displaying short messages that needs users' attention. Alert boxes will apply simple background color and padding to make the message block stand out from standard content. Use the optional <code>.accent</code>, <code>.okay</code>, <code>.warning</code>, <code>.danger</code> classes to add background colors that fit the context of the message.</p>

<br>

