<p>To help better convey the context of the message, you can add an icon to your alert message. Simply add a <a href="petalicons.html">petalicon</a> in front of your text. Wrap them around with <code>&lt;span class="alert-icon"&gt;</code> to add some margin between the icon and the text.</p>

<br>

