<p>If you want to display your alerts more prominently, there is a large variant of the alert that doubles the size of the alert icon (32px), applies color and aligns it to the left. You need the <code>.alert-icon</code> wrap for the icon, and also the <code>.alert-text</code> wrap for the text block. Insert any HTML elements you want to include in the area.</p>

<p>Note: When <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> paragraph tags are used inside alerts and they happen to be the last child of the block, bottom margin will be removed to prevent inconsistent padding for the entire alert box.</p>

